						<summary>

						<p>It records that Marudānmaiya-Vīrasuta Bhōgavarddhana-vinagata Śri Lakshaṇa Suta Srinarasingayyan made a gift of 21 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of <hi rend="italic">eḍarpuram</hi> gold for burning a perpetual lamp to Śrī Pōndaip-perumāṉaḍigaḷ at Rājamallach-chaturvēdimaṅgalam in Tiruvēgambapuṟam in Dāmark-kōṭṭam.</p>						

						<p>The <hi rend="italic">gaṇapperumakkaḷ</hi> of the temple received the amount and agreed to burn the lamp out of the interest of the endowed amount.</p>						

						</summary>
